    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_1027051068570920651.png",
                "key": "忍流飛刃斬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "忍流飛刃斬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">越祓草輪</span>。如果本角色生命值至少為6，則對自身造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">越祓草輪</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方切換角色後：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>，治療我方受傷最多的角色1點。（每回合1次）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/89377e2e3c6c55cd637d0315e24efe98_8736511482508134865.png",
                "key": "越祓雷草之輪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "越祓雷草之輪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，治療本角色2點。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/fd87e3158cbe28c54993fe1da1c54614_5230307449644872110.png",
                "key": "御詠鳴神刈山祭",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "御詠鳴神刈山祭"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著雷元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素傷害+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[激化領域]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_6351953462383395946.png",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/12/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3509001666055862185.png",
